about.summary: Multi-task Cascaded Convolutional Neural Networks for Face Detection, based on TensorFlow

name: mtcnn
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "mtcnn" %}
{% set version = "0.1.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 56624f08e088e5cf062de8005df09696cdbc0f4c2fc3578483b19e0fb3984252

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - keras >=2.0.0
    - opencv >=4.1
    - pip
    - python >=3.4
  run:
    - keras >=2.0.0
    - opencv >=4.1
    - python >=3.4

test:
  imports:
    - mtcnn
    - mtcnn.exceptions
    - mtcnn.network

about:
  home: http://github.com/ipazc/mtcnn
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: "Multi-task Cascaded Convolutional Neural Networks for Face Detection, based on TensorFlow"
  dev_url: http://github.com/ipazc/mtcnn

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - Tata17
    - oblute
    - benhuff
    - rluria14
